{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"SharedWorkerGlobalScope","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>SharedWorkerGlobalScope</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope/applicationCache\"><code>applicationCache</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope/name\"><code>name</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope/close\"><code>close()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>イベント</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope/connect_event\"><code>connect</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Web Workers API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorker\"><code>ServiceWorker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorker\"><code>SharedWorker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Worker\"><code>Worker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerLocation\"><code>WorkerLocation</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerNavigator\"><code>WorkerNavigator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><strong><code>SharedWorkerGlobalScope</code></strong> オブジェクト ( <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorker\"><code>SharedWorker</code></a> グローバルスコープ) は、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/self\" title=\"self\"><code>self</code></a> キーワードでアクセスできます。一部の追加のグローバル関数、名前空間オブジェクト、コンストラクターは、通常はワーカーのグローバルスコープに関連付けられていませんが、利用することができ、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference\">JavaScript リファレンス</a>に列挙されています。<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API/Functions_and_classes_available_to_workers\">ワーカーで利用できる機能</a>の完全なリストを参照してください。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"プロパティ","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>このインターフェイスは <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a>、またその親の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a> インターフェイスからプロパティを継承しており、したがって <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WindowTimers</code></a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WindowBase64</code></a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WindowEventHandlers\"><code>WindowEventHandlers</code></a> のプロパティを実装しています。</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"sharedworkerglobalscope.name_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope/name\"><code>SharedWorkerGlobalScope.name</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>The name that the <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorker\"><code>SharedWorker</code></a> was (optionally) given when it was created using the&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SharedWorker/SharedWorker\"><code>SharedWorker()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> constructor. This is mainly useful for debugging purposes.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sharedworkerglobalscope.applicationcache_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope/applicationCache\"><code>SharedWorkerGlobalScope.applicationCache</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>This property returns the <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\"><code>ApplicationCache</code></a> object for the worker (see <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Using_the_application_cache\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Using the application cache</a>).</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties_inherited_from_workerglobalscope","title":"WorkerGlobalScope から継承しているプロパティ","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"workerglobalscope.self\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/self\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.self</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Returns an object reference to the <code>DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope</code> object itself.</dd>\n <dt id=\"workerglobalscope.console\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/console\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.console</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns the <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/console\"><code>Console</code></a> associated with the worker.</dd>\n <dt id=\"workerglobalscope.location_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/location\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.location</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns the <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerLocation\"><code>WorkerLocation</code></a> associated with the worker. <code>WorkerLocation</code> is a specific location object, mostly a subset of the <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Location\"><code>Location</code></a> for browsing scopes, but adapted to workers.</dd>\n <dt id=\"workerglobalscope.navigator_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/navigator\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.navigator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns the <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerNavigator\"><code>WorkerNavigator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> associated with the worker. <code>WorkerNavigator</code> is a specific navigator object, mostly a subset of the <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a> for browsing scopes, but adapted to workers.</dd>\n <dt id=\"workerglobalscope.performance_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/performance_property\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.performance</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Returns the <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Performance\"><code>Performance</code></a> object associated with the worker, which is a regular performance object, but with a subset of its properties and methods available.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"event_handlers","title":"イベントハンドラー","isH3":true,"content":"<p><em>This interface inherits event handlers from the <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a> interface, and its parent <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a>, and therefore implements event handlers from <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WindowTimers</code></a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WindowBase64</code></a>, and <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WindowEventHandlers\"><code>WindowEventHandlers</code></a>.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"sharedworkerglobalscope.onconnect_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope/connect_event\"><code>SharedWorkerGlobalScope.onconnect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Is an <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> representing the code to be called when the <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/connect\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">connect</a></code> event is raised — that is, when a <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a> connection is opened between the associated <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorker\"><code>SharedWorker</code></a> and the main thread.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"メソッド","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>This interface inherits methods from the <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a> interface, and its parent <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a>, and therefore implements methods from <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WindowTimers</code></a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WindowBase64</code></a>, and <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WindowEventHandlers\"><code>WindowEventHandlers</code></a>.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"sharedworkerglobalscope.close_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope/close\"><code>SharedWorkerGlobalScope.close()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Discards any tasks queued in the <code>SharedWorkerGlobalScope</code>'s event loop, effectively closing this particular scope.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"inherited_from_workerglobalscope","title":"WorkerGlobalScope から継承したもの","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"workerglobalscope.close_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/close\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.close()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Discards any tasks queued in the <code>WorkerGlobalScope</code>'s event loop, effectively closing this particular scope.</dd>\n <dt id=\"workerglobalscope.dump_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/dump\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.dump()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Allows you to write a message to stdout — i.e. in your terminal. This is the same as Firefox's <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/dump\"><code>window.dump</code></a>, but for workers.</dd>\n <dt id=\"workerglobalscope.importscripts\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/importScripts\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.importScripts()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Imports one or more scripts into the worker's scope. You can specify as many as you'd like, separated by commas. For example:<code> importScripts('foo.js', 'bar.js');</code></dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"implemented_from_other_places","title":"他の場所から実装したもの","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"windowbase64.atob\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/atob\"><code>WindowBase64.atob()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Decodes a string of data which has been encoded using base-64 encoding.</dd>\n <dt id=\"windowbase64.btoa\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/btoa\"><code>WindowBase64.btoa()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Creates a base-64 encoded ASCII string from a string of binary data.</dd>\n <dt id=\"windowtimers.clearinterval\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/clearInterval\"><code>WindowTimers.clearInterval()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Cancels the repeated execution set using <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/setInterval\"><code>WindowTimers.setInterval()</code></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"windowtimers.cleartimeout\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/clearTimeout\"><code>WindowTimers.clearTimeout()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Cancels the repeated execution set using <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/setTimeout\"><code>WindowTimers.setTimeout()</code></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"windowtimers.setinterval\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/setInterval\"><code>WindowTimers.setInterval()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Schedules the execution of a function every X milliseconds.</dd>\n <dt id=\"windowtimers.settimeout\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/setTimeout\"><code>WindowTimers.setTimeout()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Sets a delay for executing a function.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"events","title":"イベント","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Listen to this event using <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\">addEventListener()</a></code> or by assigning an event listener to the <code>on<em>eventname</em></code> property of this interface.</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"connect\"><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope/connect_event\">connect</a></code></dt>\n <dd>Fired on shared workers when a new client connects.<br>\n Also available via the <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope/connect_event\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">onconnect (en-US)</a></code> property.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/#sharedworkerglobalscope\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ja\">SharedWorkerGlobalScope の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.SharedWorkerGlobalScope","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorker\"><code>SharedWorker</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API/Using_web_workers\">ウェブワーカーの使用</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API/Functions_and_classes_available_to_workers\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">ワーカーで使用できる関数 (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"プロパティ","id":"properties"},{"text":"メソッド","id":"methods"},{"text":"イベント","id":"events"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"SharedWorkerGlobalScope オブジェクト ( SharedWorker グローバルスコープ) は、 self キーワードでアクセスできます。一部の追加のグローバル関数、名前空間オブジェクト、コンストラクターは、通常はワーカーのグローバルスコープに関連付けられていませんが、利用することができ、 JavaScript リファレンスに列挙されています。ワーカーで利用できる機能の完全なリストを参照してください。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"SharedWorkerGlobalScope","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"SharedWorkerGlobalScope","locale":"fr","native":"Français"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/sharedworkerglobalscope","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/sharedworkerglobalscope/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope","title":"SharedWorkerGlobalScope"}],"pageTitle":"SharedWorkerGlobalScope - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}